Package: clptheory
Title: Compute Price of Production and Labor Values
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Deepankar", "Basu", , "dbasu@umass.edu", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Functions to compute the uniform rate of profit, the vector of price of 
    production and the vector of labor values; and compute measures of deviation between
    relative prices of production and relative values. You provide the input output data and 
    'clptheory' does the calculations for you.
